io.netty.util.collection

Interface ShortObjectMap<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the value type stored in the map.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Map<Short,V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ShortObjectHashMap

    public interface ShortObjectMap<V>
extends Map<Short,V>
    Interface for a primitive map that uses shorts as keys.

      • entries

        Iterable<ShortObjectMap.PrimitiveEntry<V>> entries()
        Gets an iterable to traverse over the primitive entries contained in this map. As an optimization, the ShortObjectMap.PrimitiveEntrys returned by the Iterator may change as the Iterator progresses. The caller should not rely on ShortObjectMap.PrimitiveEntry key/value stability.
